data.title: Bahia de Algeciras CCGT Power Plant Spain
meta_keywords: Bahia de Algeciras CCGT Power Plant Spain Andalusia Spain
data.meta_description: Bahia de Algeciras CCGT Power Plant Spain is located at Puente Mayorga industrial area, Campo de Gibraltar, Cadiz, Andalusia, Spain. Location coordinates are: Latitude= 36.1829, Longitude= -5.3905. This infrastructure is of TYPE Gas Power Plant with a design capacity of 800 MWe. It has 3 unit(s). The first unit was commissioned in 2011 and the last in 2011. It is operated by E.ON Espana.
